  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 4th level, a desert druid ignores the effects of a hot climate\
    \ as if using endure elements. She also has a reduced need to eat and drink, as\
    \ if wearing a ring of sustenance (though normal sleep is still required).\nThis\
    \ ability replaces resist nature's lure."
